sequenceDiagram
  participant P as Public/Admin App
  participant A as API
  participant D as MongoDB
  participant R as R2

  P->>A: Request public or private resource
  A->>D: Validate tenant-scoped data
  A-->>P: Return business response
  P->>A: Upload media request
  A->>R: Store normalized asset
  A-->>P: Return asset reference
